{"about_the_game":"<strong>Embark on a haunting journey in Ontotis, where chilling secrets of the past shape a story that blurs reality and nightmare in this psychological horror experience.</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/ontotis_info_logo.gif?t=1730737334\" /><br><br><strong><u>Key Features</u></strong><br><br>\u2756  Engage in an immersive gameplay experience that blends an atmospheric environment with chilling horror elements.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/ontotis_info.gif?t=1730737334\" /><br><br>\u2756  Solve intricate puzzles to progress the story and unlock secrets.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/ontotis_info3.gif?t=1730737334\" /><br><br>\u2756  Piece together the mystery by discovering scattered items and pages that hold crucial clues within the game.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/ontotis_info2.gif?t=1730737334\" /><br><br>\u2756  Explore different endings based on the items used and mysteries unraveled.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/ontotis_info4.gif?t=1730737334\" /><br><br><br><strong><u>Story</u></strong><br>You take the role of Robert, a man grappling with the loss of his wife Joann, as he takes on a remote job as a caretaker for abandoned homes during the winter/fall season in search of peace and solitude. However, as a severe storm approaches, you are tasked with securing one final property on the hill. <br>As you secure the house and complete your chores, strange occurrences and unexplained phenomena come to light, along with a mysterious figure that seems linked to the events at hand. <br>Through examination of various objects and clues within the property, you begin to realize that a sinister presence may be at play, leading to a series of unsettling events during your stay as you try to piece together the mystery of the former residents of the house.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Page Perfectionist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2484500/1cc25e583300f90e45bfa1cd94d5e865a2377ba1.jpg"},{"name":"Cassette Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2484500/694e4a94aa45867422986ccb976090c0597ed75e.jpg"},{"name":"Cosmic Horrors","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2484500/dd003adb553e7232a3e769fcf8d92471e29d045f.jpg"},{"name":"Eerie Echoes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2484500/deb13e2d9268c08dafb9ed28624bf87598fc9737.jpg"},{"name":"Mothman's Prophecy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2484500/d5bd96732cb65edf5421349435ef48b2b4f89f19.jpg"},{"name":"Moving Forward","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2484500/5594e74a5ac636761c4fe1c0b82bd61aba6cb529.jpg"},{"name":"Eternal Reunion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2484500/600809c81d01688cff71d39baf564f05a51896e7.jpg"},{"name":"A Grave Revelation","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2484500/c03734e8216bea802d3d8254f37b9fe7e02b6c7a.jpg"},{"name":"Chore Champion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2484500/6587dbc2866d24a6db0d0ebed8af2335380e2bcd.jpg"}],"total":9},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730737334","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/page.bg.jpg?t=1730737334","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.co